data.eml:eml: The fishes of St Helena Island, central Atlantic Ocean-new records and an annotated check-list

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Brown, Judith, Beard, Annalea, Clingham, Elizabeth, Fricke, Ronald, Henry, Leeann, Wirtz, Peter (2019): The fishes of St Helena Island, central Atlantic Ocean-new records and an annotated check-list. Zootaxa 4543 (2): 151-194, DOI: https://doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4543.2.1
